We shared the same bed for years.

297
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,700
If anyone knows you best,

298
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:11,860
it's me.

299
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:15,900
Back then,

300
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,420
