435
00:24:06,540 --> 00:24:07,300
That's a deal.

436
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:18,500
Just wait a little longer.

437
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:22,700
I'll make sure you have a better life.

438
00:24:24,580 --> 00:24:26,820
