449
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,500
You're still young.

450
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,260
You can't spend your whole life
with just a dog

451
00:24:57,260 --> 00:24:58,300
and a blind man.

452
00:24:58,900 --> 00:25:01,540
