00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:27,340
What's the matter?

480
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,740
Who's really guilty here?

481
00:27:31,540 --> 00:27:32,140
What?

482
00:27:32,420 --> 00:27:33,700
So you've been into me

483
